function.name: dist_CDFProb
function.doc: dist_CDFProb computes the Cumulative Destribution Function of distribution d..

return.doc: the Cumulative Destribution Function value for a certain distribution d.

function.name: dist_CheckDist
function.doc: dist_CheckDist verifies if a certain given distribution value belongs to the existing distribution enumeration.

return.doc: "OK" if the value belongs to the enumeration, otherwise returns "ERR".

argument.name: d
argument.doc: is a distribution value to be checked if it is valid.

function.name: dist_PDFProb
function.doc: dist_PDFProb computes the Probability Density Function of distribution d..

return.doc: the Probability Density Function value for a certain distribution d.
